{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Code Me, dsewnr","author":"dsewnr"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"cc3411d3-d284-5d2b-8c3b-4b85514668b6","excerpt":"米家檯燈 Pro 已經開完箱 (有開客廳大燈) 用了 7 年左右的工作檯燈掛掉好一陣子了，說是掛掉不太精確，其實是控制不住它了… 插著電的情況下有時候沒人去開它會自動開起來，想開的時候試遍各種方法怎麼開就是不亮，大概就是這種失控的情況。 趁著沒啥優惠感的 1111，用了張無感的優惠券在 111…","html":"<h3>米家檯燈 Pro 已經開完箱 (有開客廳大燈)</h3>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 720px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 75%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"mi adjustable smart desk lamp 0\"\n        title=\"mi adjustable smart desk lamp 0\"\n        src=\"/static/687b1f6787301f2e2d48f41bd32599af/8a6f4/mi-adjustable-smart-desk-lamp-0.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/687b1f6787301f2e2d48f41bd32599af/51f8b/mi-adjustable-smart-desk-lamp-0.jpg 180w,\n/static/687b1f6787301f2e2d48f41bd32599af/5aea8/mi-adjustable-smart-desk-lamp-0.jpg 360w,\n/static/687b1f6787301f2e2d48f41bd32599af/8a6f4/mi-adjustable-smart-desk-lamp-0.jpg 720w,\n/static/687b1f6787301f2e2d48f41bd32599af/72109/mi-adjustable-smart-desk-lamp-0.jpg 1080w,\n/static/687b1f6787301f2e2d48f41bd32599af/92a9d/mi-adjustable-smart-desk-lamp-0.jpg 1280w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<hr>\n<p>用了 7 年左右的工作檯燈掛掉好一陣子了，說是掛掉不太精確，其實是控制不住它了… 插著電的情況下有時候沒人去開它會自動開起來，想開的時候試遍各種方法怎麼開就是不亮，大概就是這種失控的情況。</p>\n<p>趁著沒啥優惠感的 1111，用了張無感的優惠券在 1111 忍痛下訂了(隔天收到)，為了湊優惠券的使用限制還多訂了一個自拍棒(還在路上)，打算拿來當手機架視訊通話用，平時就可以給家人使用，應該不會變成垃圾吧 XD</p>\n<hr>\n<h3>Apple Homekit 初體驗</h3>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 591px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 216.58206429780034%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"mi adjustable smart desk lamp 1\"\n        title=\"mi adjustable smart desk lamp 1\"\n        src=\"/static/4ccdfa549d3496d274224cb56228f95e/2041f/mi-adjustable-smart-desk-lamp-1.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/4ccdfa549d3496d274224cb56228f95e/fb98e/mi-adjustable-smart-desk-lamp-1.jpg 180w,\n/static/4ccdfa549d3496d274224cb56228f95e/3c530/mi-adjustable-smart-desk-lamp-1.jpg 360w,\n/static/4ccdfa549d3496d274224cb56228f95e/2041f/mi-adjustable-smart-desk-lamp-1.jpg 591w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 591px) 100vw, 591px\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<hr>\n<h3>手機直接控制亮度、色溫超級方便der</h3>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 591px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 216.58206429780034%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"mi adjustable smart desk lamp 2\"\n        title=\"mi adjustable smart desk lamp 2\"\n        src=\"/static/1bafbe3258a37704ed5b412b0b441251/2041f/mi-adjustable-smart-desk-lamp-2.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/1bafbe3258a37704ed5b412b0b441251/fb98e/mi-adjustable-smart-desk-lamp-2.jpg 180w,\n/static/1bafbe3258a37704ed5b412b0b441251/3c530/mi-adjustable-smart-desk-lamp-2.jpg 360w,\n/static/1bafbe3258a37704ed5b412b0b441251/2041f/mi-adjustable-smart-desk-lamp-2.jpg 591w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 591px) 100vw, 591px\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<hr>\n<h3>睡前工作區來一杯 (已關客廳大燈)</h3>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 720px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 75%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"mi adjustable smart desk lamp 3\"\n        title=\"mi adjustable smart desk lamp 3\"\n        src=\"/static/510ca92f518f9a2c07523242e42eb2d2/8a6f4/mi-adjustable-smart-desk-lamp-3.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/510ca92f518f9a2c07523242e42eb2d2/51f8b/mi-adjustable-smart-desk-lamp-3.jpg 180w,\n/static/510ca92f518f9a2c07523242e42eb2d2/5aea8/mi-adjustable-smart-desk-lamp-3.jpg 360w,\n/static/510ca92f518f9a2c07523242e42eb2d2/8a6f4/mi-adjustable-smart-desk-lamp-3.jpg 720w,\n/static/510ca92f518f9a2c07523242e42eb2d2/72109/mi-adjustable-smart-desk-lamp-3.jpg 1080w,\n/static/510ca92f518f9a2c07523242e42eb2d2/92a9d/mi-adjustable-smart-desk-lamp-3.jpg 1280w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<hr>\n<p>附帶一提，買之前沒特別注意重量，這燈手感還蠻重的，在我意料之外。目前對這光質、亮度、範圍、機構、操作…等都還蠻滿意的，希望它能活的久一點啊！接下來買日常用品應該都要來注意一下有沒有支援 Apple Homekit 了！</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"米家檯燈 Pro 沒有開箱","date":"November 12, 2019"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/mi-adjustable-smart-desk-lamp/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/pythonista-for-mcdonald-app/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"抽麥當勞快速鍵"}},"next":null}}